    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "四一二政变后各方的应对",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300068898_8_9906-9949",
          "range": "9906-9949",
          "rangeStart": 9906,
          "rangeEnd": 9949,
          "markText": "第一，很直接的原因还是经济问题。冯玉祥说：“我们所感到的困难，主要地是在财政方面。”他",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1723718590,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-15 18:43:10",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300068898&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9906&rangeEnd=9949",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f3f32fe0813ab8169g018d97?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9906&rangeEnd=9949"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300068898_8_10859-10902",
          "range": "10859-10902",
          "rangeStart": 10859,
          "rangeEnd": 10902,
          "markText": "第二，从更深层次来看，冯玉祥不是共产主义者，只能说是一个信奉孙中山三民主义的爱国军人。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1723718586,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-15 18:43:06",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300068898&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10859&rangeEnd=10902",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f3f32fe0813ab8169g018d97?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10859&rangeEnd=10902"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300068898_8_2377-2427",
          "range": "2377-2427",
          "rangeStart": 2377,
          "rangeEnd": 2427,
          "markText": "一几乎没有军队，二没有政权，三对农民的力量和作用估计过低，没有将渴望得到土地的农民充分组织和武装起来",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1723718585,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-15 18:43:05",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300068898&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2377&rangeEnd=2427",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f3f32fe0813ab8169g018d97?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2377&rangeEnd=2427"
        }
      ]
    },
